<h1 class="font-weight-bold">Towns at SOUTH ALEX®</h1>
<p class="mt-2 font-weight-bold">INCREDIBLY WELL-LOCATED 4-LEVEL TOWNHOMES IN SOUTH ALEXANDRIA
</p>
<p>When you live at the corner of South Kings Highway and Poag Street, you live in the center of South Alexandria. Say
    goodbye to long commutes and embrace a life where work, shopping, dining, & entertainment are all just moments away.
    Coming Soon & Under Construction – South Alex® Retail with Aldi Grocery, Boutiques, Restaurants and more!</p>
<p class="mt-2">Craftmark Homes, one of the largest privately-owned home builders in the D.C. Metro area, is excited to
    feature architecturally distinct 4-level, 2-Car Garage Townhomes with scenic Rooftop Terraces and Private
    Bedroom/Bath Lofts in Alexandria, Virginia. All of this in the center of the long-awaited 10-acre mixed-use
    redevelopment of the Penn-Daw Area. Work, play, and live at the intersection of a vivacious life and your everyday
    needs - at your doorstep.</p>
<p class="mt-2">Live in the center of it all, just a 10-minute drive to Old Town Alexandria and a 10-minute walk to the
    Huntington Metro Station that's just a few stops to Washington D.C. Travel is made easy with nearby Reagan National
    Airport (DCA). South Alex® is just minutes from the D.C. Metro’s major employment hubs - Amazon HQ2, The Pentagon,
    Fort Belvoir, Tysons Corner, Joint Base Andrews and Downtown D. C. Regional bike trails are conveniently integrated
    nearby, as is an adjacent Metro bus stop.</p>
<p class="mt-2">Live within a vibrant mix of distinctive shops, restaurants, and residences in an art-inspired setting
    of bright community spaces, all conveniently located in the heart of South Alexandria. Enjoy culture, nightlife, and
    great cuisine minutes from your home. Or relax in your new Craftmark townhome and take in scenic views from your
    rooftop terrace. Parks, play areas, and dog parks are at your fingertips. Enjoy urban conveniences without
    sacrificing suburban comforts!</p>
